Although the SceneReplication sample works well, the server instance is not able to join as a client whilst hosting a local server. 

Whether or not this is a limitation is unclear, however something like this would be sufficient:-

```c++
void SceneReplication::HandleStartServer(StringHash eventType, VariantMap& eventData)
{
    Network* network = GetSubsystem<Network>();
    network->StartServer(SERVER_PORT);

    network->Connect(String("localhost"), SERVER_PORT, scene_);

    UpdateButtons();
}
```

